 before you head off. <br><br>There can be some conflicting information online, so make sure you check the source of the info. Ours comes from the<a href="http://www.thaiembassy.org/london/en/services/7747/86207-Prohibition-of-e-cigarettes.html" target="_self"> Royal Thai Embassy, London</a>.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 11.5px;"><div class="pf-097be1f1 sc-iGPElx fTEkif" data-pf-type="Column"><picture class="pf-99d916f6 sc-fZwumE iCGEPP" data-pf-type="Image"><source media="(min-width: 1200px)" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited_400x3000.jpg?61102"><source media="(min-width: 992px) and (max-width: 1199px)" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited.jpg?61102"><source media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px)" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited.jpg?61102"><source media="(max-width: 767px) and (orientation: portrait)" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited_400x300.jpg?61102&resized 1x, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited_850x850.jpg?61102&resized 2x"><source media="(max-width: 767px) and (orientation: landscape)" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited_400x300.jpg?61102&resized 1x, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/t/62/assets/pf-bb34f890-271b-4302-b4f0-82529fcfba67--vape-in-Thailand-Edited-Edited-Edited.jpg?61102 2x"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0290/5629/